name: GigaDetection: Object Detection meets Gigapixel Videography(赛季 1)
description: 本大赛挑战的任务是多目标检测（行人和车辆）。给定一个静态的十亿像素图像，参与者需要检测两种类型的对象：行人和车辆。每个行人包括三个检测框，即可见边界框、全身边界框和头部边界框。对于每一辆车，需要可见的边界框进行评估。

name: Radiant Earth Spot the Crop Challenge
description: Based on time-series of Sentinel-2 satellite images can you classify crop types in South Africa?

name: Radiant Earth Spot the Crop XL Challenge
description: Based on time-series of Sentinel-1 and Sentinel-2 satellite images can you classify crop types in South Africa?
